# Habit Tracker (CLI)

Features: add habits, mark done, list, dashboard (stale detection), JSON storage.

## Run
```bash
python cli.py            # start the app
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
pip install -r requirements.txt
pytest -q

